            mc"No, it‚Äôs perfect."
            show sc w2eveready e12
            mc"Wow‚Ä¶"
            show sc w2eveready e13
            $ s_points = change_stat(s_points,2,s_name)
            s"(YES! He likes it! I knew he would.)" # +2 FRIEND PTS"
        "It‚Äôs a bit much":
            mc"Well‚Ä¶"
            show sc w2eveready e04
            s"Oh, it‚Äôs a bit much, isn‚Äôt it?"
            mc"It might be, it‚Äôs hard to say."
            show sc w2eveready e02
            mc"I‚Äôm also not quite sure what would be considered appropriate attire for this thing."
            $ s_points = change_stat(s_points,-2,s_name)
            mc"The twins could‚Äôve given us some more details though." #-2 FRIEND PTS"
            show sc w2eveready e04
            s"Yeah, they could have."
            # (scene continues)"
    show sc w2eveready e03
    s"You look very handsome [y_name]. I‚Äôm sure you‚Äôll turn heads when we arrive."
    show sc w2eveready e08
    mc"Haha, unlikely! But thanks."
    show sc w2eveready e05
    s"Come on, we better get going. We don‚Äôt want Ivy and Lily to think we‚Äôve stood them up!"
    show sc w2eveready e03
    mc"Haha, true that!"
