label lb_w2_mow_c_crying:
    if _in_replay:
        if y_name == None:
            $ y_name = "MC"
        else:
            $ y_name = persistent.y_name

        if s_name == None:
            $ s_name = "S"
        else:
            $ s_name = persistent.s_name

        if c_name == None:
            $ c_name = "Shortcake"
        else:
            $ c_name = persistent.c_name

        show screen toprightmenu

        play music "music/01/2936-fliegen-by-sascha-ende.mp3"
    # (She has her head in her hands, still upset)"
    play ambient "sound effects/01/01/Birds_in_trees_sounds_effects1.mp3" loop fadeout 1.0 fadein 1.0
    scene sc w2cfrontdesk f87
    with dissolve
    mc"Are you all right [c_name]? Are you gonna be okay?"
    c"Yeah, I‚Äôm sure I‚Äôll be fine."
    show sc w2cfrontdesk f89
    c"It just became really stressful being in there, and I couldn‚Äôt handle it."
    show sc w2cfrontdesk f88
    c"I‚Äôm sorry for screwing up [y_name]. I just didn‚Äôt know what to say back to [s_name]."
    show sc w2cfrontdesk f87
    c"I know she was only playing a role, but some of the things she said were ultra harsh."
    show sc w2cfrontdesk f88
    mc"I completely agree, she was out of line."
    c"(Sigh‚Ä¶)"
    show sc w2cfrontdesk f89
    c"If that‚Äôs what her hotel guests are really like, then I don‚Äôt think I‚Äôll be able to cope."
    show sc w2cfrontdesk f88
    c"I think it was a mistake to come here today."
    show sc w2cfrontdesk f87
    c"My Mom is going to hate me for giving up so easily though, that is, if I even tell her why I quit."
    show sc w2cfrontdesk f100
    mc"Look, don‚Äôt worry about it [c_name]."
    mc"I thought you did a great job and I just told [s_name] that she overdid things in there."
    mc"But I know that she regrets putting you through all of that. I‚Äôm proud of you just for giving it a go."
    # (C hugs the MC)"
    show sc w2cfrontdesk f101
    c"Thanks [y_name]. In a lot of ways, I feel like I really let you down more than anything."
    show sc w2cfrontdesk f102
    show screen scr_rewards("sc w2cfrontdesk f102b","v_rewards_c_24")
    mc"Nah‚Ä¶ I don‚Äôt think you could ever do that [c_name]."
    # (C and the MC break their hug, then she looks into his eyes)"
    hide screen scr_rewards
    show sc w2cfrontdesk f103
    mc"(At least she‚Äôs stopped crying now, and seems a little happier.)"
    c"‚Ä¶"
    mc"What is it [c_name]?"
    show sc w2cfrontdesk f104
    c"Your eyes. I never realised just how blue they were until now."
    mc"Well you know what they say about people with blue eyes?"
    show sc w2cfrontdesk f103
    c"No, what?"
    mc"Those that possess them are quite knowledgable, and they have a calm and peaceful personality."
    show sc w2cfrontdesk f104
    c"Oh, well I definitely feel that whenever I‚Äôm around you. And you‚Äôre quite smart too!"
    show sc w2cfrontdesk f126
    c"Mwah!"
    mc"(Ohh!!)"
    # (cousin and the MC look and smile at each other, possible romantic moment. They are then interrupted by friend)"
    show sc w2cfrontdesk f107
    s"[c_name], there you are!"
    s"Oh sweetie, I'm so sorry for everything that happened just now."
    s"I didn‚Äôt realise just how harsh and incredibly thoughtless I was being to you."
    show sc w2cfrontdesk f96
    s"Can you ever forgive me?"
    show sc w2cfrontdesk f99
    c"Yes, of course I will [s_name]."
    # (Friend and cousin hug)"
    show sc w2cfrontdesk f107
    s"I promise not to ever do anything like that to you again."
    s"You‚Äôre like a little sister to me, and when you‚Äôre upset, I‚Äôm upset."
    show sc w2cfrontdesk f97
    c"It‚Äôs okay, really, I‚Äôm fine."
    show sc w2cfrontdesk f106
    s"So, did you want to still want to work with me and [y_name]?"
    show sc w2cfrontdesk f99
    c"Uh, I think I may have to pass on the job guys."
    c"I thought I‚Äôd be more than capable of doing this kind of work, but maybe I‚Äôm not quite ready yet."
    show sc w2cfrontdesk f93
    mc"That‚Äôs okay. Like we said to you before, no pressure at all, right [s_name]?"
    show sc w2cfrontdesk f107
    s"Yes, of course."
    show sc w2cfrontdesk f106
    s"But I still want to make things up to you [c_name]."
    s"Are you doing anything right now?"
    show sc w2cfrontdesk f96
    c"I don‚Äôt have any plans, no."
    show sc w2cfrontdesk f105
    s"Okay, well I have to go into town to get a few things from the mall. Why don‚Äôt you come with me?"
    show sc w2cfrontdesk f108
    s"There‚Äôs a double-stack of ice cream in it for you."
    show sc w2cfrontdesk f95
    c"Oh, well count me in!"
    show sc w2cfrontdesk f105
    s"Great!"
    show sc w2cfrontdesk f112
    s"Did you want to join us [y_name]?"
    show sc w2cfrontdesk f110
    mc"Uh, I would have definitely been keen, but I just received a text message from [k_name], Ivy and Lily‚Äôs little sister."
    mc"She asked if she could come around to take a look at the events hall to get a better idea of the changes that we would like her to make."
    mc"And I‚Äôve already agreed to it. So she‚Äôll be here in about fifteen minutes."
    show sc w2cfrontdesk f112
    s"Oh, no problems at all."
    s"That‚Äôs pretty important so while you‚Äôre taking care of that, [c_name] and I will be at the mall."
    s"We can catch up on a few things when I return."
    mc"No sweat."
    show sc w2cfrontdesk f115
    c"Thanks for your advice [y_name]."
    show sc w2cfrontdesk f121
    c"Actually, thanks to both of you. What happened in the hotel reception area has been a real eye-opener for me."
    show sc w2cfrontdesk f116
    c"And I really appreciate you both trying to help."
    mc"It‚Äôs our pleasure [c_name]."
    show sc w2cfrontdesk f114
    mc"And if you change your mind, we‚Äôll have a badge with your name on it waiting for you. Won‚Äôt we [s_name]?"
    show sc w2cfrontdesk f115
    s"Yes, we certainly will."
    show sc w2cfrontdesk f108
    s"Come on, let‚Äôs head back to the hotel and grab my scooter to ride into town."
    stop ambient fadeout 1.0
    # (friend and cousin hold hands and head back to the hotel with the MC trailing behind them)"
    if _in_replay:
        scene black
        with dissolve
        scene black
        with Pause (2)
    $ persistent.replay_w2_mow_c_crying = False
    $ renpy.end_replay()
    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)













label lb_w2_kris_event_hall:
    # Day 4 (MOW) 18 - Kristina arrives to look over the events hall with the MC"
    # SCENE BEGINS"
    # (MC sits behind the reception desk at the computer, typing away, waiting for Kristina to arrive)"
    scene sc w2krishall k04
    with dissolve
    mc"(There, this should be up-to-date now.)"
    show sc w2krishall k06
    if persistent.v_xray_enabled:
        show screen scr_peeping_tom("sc w2krishall k06","sc w2krishall k06x","v_pt_image_index_w2_27")
    k"So... This is the Sunshine Bay Lighthouse Hotel."
    # (MC looks up, and sees Kristina standing before the counter)"
    mc"Huh?"
    hide screen scr_peeping_tom
    show sc w2krishall k03
    # ROLLING WIP OF KRISTINA (Kristina arrives in casual clothing, conversation)"
    mc"Oh, hey [k_name]. Sorry, I was just finishing up here."
    # (MC stands up and greets Kristina)"
    # [Hug her / Kiss her on the cheek / Do nothing]"
    show sc w2krishall k07
    k"I don‚Äôt have much time, but I thought I‚Äôd quickly come and check out the hotel events room you were telling me about."
    mc"Oh right, yes. Come with me and I can show you the room now‚Ä¶"
    show sc w2krishall k09
    k"Great!"
    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)

    # (MC and Kristina in the events hall)"
    scene sc w2krishall k23
    with dissolve
    mc"This is it. So what are your first impressions?"
    show sc w2krishall k19
    k"Hmm‚Ä¶ It‚Äôs a very nice room, lots of space and I can tell that it‚Äôs hosted all kinds of events and parties in the past."
    show sc w2krishall k17
    k"However, at first glance, it does seem like this room hasn‚Äôt been renovated for several years."
    show sc w2krishall k18
    k"So the things I‚Äôd be looking to change would be the lighting, as the fixtures look very outdated and you could do with a more modern look in here."
    show sc w2krishall k13
    k"I‚Äôd also consider changing the colour of the walls, just to liven things up a bit."
    show sc w2krishall k20
    k"And your flooring could do with a change too."
    show sc w2krishall k13
    mc"Oh, are you saying that the tiles would need to be ripped up and completely replaced?"
    show sc w2krishall k15
    k"No, you don‚Äôt need to do that. That would be too expensive, and I know you‚Äôre working with a budget."
    show sc w2krishall k13
    k"You can just make minor changes, add designs to the tiles rather than completely changing them."
    show sc w2krishall k14
    k"Realistically you could have this room updated and ready to host events within two weeks, maybe less."
    show sc w2krishall k13
    mc"Okay‚Ä¶So if you were to work with us, how much would you want to be paid for a job like this [k_name]?"
    show sc w2krishall k19
    k"Nothing."
    show sc w2krishall k14
    if persistent.v_xray_enabled:
        show screen scr_peeping_tom("sc w2krishall k14","sc w2krishall k14x","v_pt_image_index_w2_28")
    mc"Nothing? What do you mean nothing?"
    k"Well, my course requires that I show an example of either designing or re-designing a room, and this is the ideal situation for me."
    k"I would require certain materials though, and some of those are readily available to me at college that I can use here."
    mc"That‚Äôs fantastic [k_name]."
    hide screen scr_peeping_tom
    show sc w2krishall k13
    mc"I‚Äôm sure [s_name] will be able to supply you with some funds for whatever else you need."
    mc"And if you do a good job, there‚Äôs a chance that she‚Äôll also ask you to have a look at the current hotel room designs for your own personal input."
    mc"I think she mentioned wanting to change all of the rooms up as well."
    show sc w2krishall k19
    k"Look, I‚Äôd really love to help you both out in some way. However, there‚Äôs a catch."
    show sc w2krishall k14
    mc"A catch?"
    k"Yes. If I do this for you, I want something in return."
    k"I mean, I‚Äôm offering to do an upgrade on this room for nothing, and also giving up some of my time."


    if v_w2_k_deal:
        #‚ÄúAdd these lines if the player chose MAKE A DEAL when they spoke with Kristina earlier in the update‚Äù
        show sc w2krishall k13
        mc"I hardly think that you‚Äôre doing this for nothing [k_name]."
        mc"I mean, we already agreed upon having a night out in town together, did we not?"
        show sc w2krishall k14
        k"That‚Äôs true, but I need one more small favour from you before I agree to do the work that you require from me [y_name]."
        mc"(Sigh‚Ä¶)"
        mc"(She certainly is a cunning little minx‚Ä¶)"
    else:
        #‚ÄúAdd these lines if the player chose REFUSE HER DEAL when they spoke with Kristina earlier in the update‚Äù
        show sc w2krishall k14
        mc"(Sigh‚Ä¶ She certainly is a cunning little minx‚Ä¶)"
        mc"(I probably should‚Äôve known that [k_name] doing this job for nothing was too good to be true.)"


    show sc w2krishall k13
    mc"Okay, so what exactly do you want [k_name]?"
    mc"Free accommodation, access to the health centre or pool area whenever you want?"
    show sc w2krishall k15
    k"No, not quite. I need your help again with something at the church."
    show sc w2krishall k13
    mc"(Oh boy‚Ä¶ What is she going to get me to do this time?)"
    mc"Okay, what do you need from me?"
    show sc w2krishall k18
    k"I only have my suspicions at the moment, but I think something unusual is taking place at our church after hours."
    show sc w2krishall k13
    mc"What do you mean by unusual?"
    k"Well you know how my father is the minister?"
    mc"Yeah, what about him?"
    show sc w2krishall k15
    k"He didn‚Äôt come home for dinner one night and I told my Mom that I would go and see him at the church, just to see if he was okay."
    k"When I arrived there, his office door was locked."
    k"I knocked on his door and when he opened it, he had this panic-stricken look on his face, and he was sweating profusely."
    show sc w2krishall k13
    mc"Did you ask him about it?"
    show sc w2krishall k18
    k"No I didn‚Äôt."
    k"Before I had a chance to ask him, he told me to go away, stating that he was attending to some important business and that he wouldn't be coming home until late."
    k"I found this to be really strange because my father has never spoken to me like that before."
    show sc w2krishall k13
    mc"When was this?"
    k"A few weeks ago. He never talked to me about that night, and he‚Äôs been acting as though it never even happened."
    mc"Has he been coming home for dinner every night since?"
    show sc w2krishall k15
    k"Yes he has. Well, except for Friday nights I‚Äôve noticed."
    k"He doesn‚Äôt come home until very late on those nights as well."
    k"He‚Äôs been telling my Mom that he stays late to organise his weekend sermons."
    show sc w2krishall k13
    mc"But you don‚Äôt believe him?"
    k"Well, I decided to go to the church last Friday night, just to see if he was indeed working on his sermons."
    k"When I arrived, sure enough, he was there, but in one of the other offices this time."
    k"And this time, he was sitting behind his desk, all relaxed, and everything seemed normal."
    k"He had a very pleasant look on his face, like he was in absolute bliss."
    mc"(Hmm‚Ä¶ I feel like I‚Äôve heard this story before.)"
    mc"What happened next?"
    show sc w2krishall k17
    k"Father David arrived, closed the door, and I‚Äôm not entirely sure what happened after that."
    show sc w2krishall k13
    mc"Did you put your ear to the door to try and listen in on their conversation?"
    k"Yeah I did. At first, it sounded like a normal conversation between my Dad and father David."
    k"But then I heard the voice of a woman."
    mc"A woman? Could it have been one of the nuns?"
    show sc w2krishall k15
    k"Unlikely. As I‚Äôve said to you before, women are not allowed in any of the main office rooms."
    mc"Did you find anything else out?"
    k"Unfortunately no. I heard someone coming, so I quickly scurried out of there without being noticed."
    mc"Okay, well what is it that you want me to do [k_name]?"
    show sc w2krishall k13
    k"I want you to find out what my father is up to [y_name]."
    mc"What is it that you think your father is involved in?"
    show sc w2krishall k18
    k"Honestly?"
    k"I think he or one of the other priests organise secret orgies behind closed doors every now and then."
    # (screen shakes)"
    show sc w2krishall k15
    with vpunch
    mc"Oh my god! Are you serious? That seems a little far-fetched, don‚Äôt you think?"
    k"Not at all. I just need some proof that clears my father of any wrongdoing."
    k"If it‚Äôs one of the other priests and my Dad isn‚Äôt involved, then I‚Äôd like to catch them out."
    k"But as I said, I need your help."

    if v_day3_church_steal_photo:
        # ‚ÄúAdd these lines if the player chose to COPY THE PHOTO in the last update‚Äù"
        mc"Hang on a second‚Ä¶"
        show sc w2krishall k17
        mc"I have something that you might be interested in seeing. Give me a moment here to find it for you."
        k"What do you have there [y_name]?"
        show sc w2krishall k26
        mc"I found this when I was looking for the keys to your father‚Äôs secret office."
        # (Kristina looks at the photo, look of shock on her face)"
        show sc w2krishall k21
        k"Oh my god! That‚Äôs father David!"
        show sc w2krishall k15
        mc"Do you recognise the two women in the photo?"
        show sc w2krishall k26
        k"No, I‚Äôve never seen them before."
        k"Hey‚Ä¶ What did you take a photo of this for?"
        show sc w2krishall k15
        mc"Uh‚Ä¶ No reason."
        show sc w2krishall k13
        mc"I guess I thought at the time that it could be important for something, given that it was hidden underneath the drawer of your father‚Äôs work desk."
        show sc w2krishall k14
        $ k_points = change_stat(k_points,2,k_name)
        k"Hmm‚Ä¶ That makes sense. Good thinking [y_name]." #+2 KRISTINA POINTS"
        show sc w2krishall k18
        k"But this doesn‚Äôt prove that my father is involved in any of these late-night sessions. So, will you still help me?"
    show sc w2krishall k13
    mc"Okay, I‚Äôll see what I can do. When would you like me to help you though?"
    show sc w2krishall k14
    k"Since you're busy with the wedding this weekend, perhaps it would be best if you were to meet me somewhere next week on Friday, after sundown, and then we can go to the church together."
    show sc w2krishall k13
    mc"What did you have in mind, exactly?"
    if v_day3_church_late == False:
        # ‚ÄúIf the player was on the early path in the last update‚Äù"
        show sc w2krishall k14
        k"What I was thinking is that I could provide you with a priest's outfit beforehand."
        k"That way, you can move around the church without it looking suspicious."
        mc"Me? Dressed as a priest? Hmm‚Ä¶ I don‚Äôt know."
        mc"(That sounds like a ridiculous idea.)"
        k"Trust me, it will work."
        k"My father told me this morning that they‚Äôre expecting a Father Ted, who is from another church, to arrive at the church sometime next week."
        k"They‚Äôve never met him before nor do they know what he looks like."
        show sc w2krishall k16
        k"So if anyone asks, you could be Father Ted for the short time that you‚Äôre in there."
        show sc w2krishall k14
        mc"(Damn. It looks like there‚Äôs no way out of this now, especially if I want [k_name] to help me and [s_name] out with changing the events hall setup.)"
        mc"All right, as much as I‚Äôm against this idea, I‚Äôll do it."
    else:
        # ‚ÄúIf the player was on the late path in the last update‚Äù"
        show sc w2krishall k14
        k"What I was thinking is that I could provide you with a priest's outfit, so you can reprise your role as Father Ted again!"
        mc"Oh, again??"
        mc"(Not again‚Ä¶)"
        show sc w2krishall k16
        k"Yeah, it‚Äôs perfect! And you were really convincing last time [y_name]."
        show sc w2krishall k13
        mc"I don‚Äôt know [k_name]. We got pretty lucky I think."
        show sc w2krishall k14
        k"Trust me, it will work. I mean, you‚Äôve pretty much earned Father David‚Äôs trust, so that‚Äôs a good start."
        mc"(Damn. It looks like there‚Äôs no way out of this now, especially if I want [k_name] to help me and [s_name] out with changing the events hall setup.)"
        mc"All right, as much as I‚Äôm against this idea, I‚Äôll do it."
    # (scene continues)"
    show sc w2krishall k16
    k"Awesome!"
    show sc w2krishall k24
    mc"(I wonder why she‚Äôs so desperate to find out what her father gets up to every Friday night?)"
    mc"(I would have thought that discovering that he‚Äôs potentially involved with other women, would be quite upsetting for [k_name].)"
    mc"(But it sure doesn‚Äôt feel like that‚Äôs how she sees things.)"
    show sc w2krishall k19
    k"And if you do this for me [y_name], then I promise you that a very special treat will be coming your way."
    show sc w2krishall k24
    mc"A special treat? Like what?"
    # [Use your imagination / Don‚Äôt use it]"
    menu:
        "Use your imagination"(wt="Best choice"):
            show sc w2krishall k19
            k"Use your imagination [y_name]‚Ä¶"
            # (Kristina‚Äôs dress disappears so that she‚Äôs standing before the MC in a bra and panties)"
            show sc w2krishall k34
            with flash
            mc"Whoah‚Ä¶" #+2 KRISTINA POINTS"
            $ k_points = change_stat(k_points,2,k_name)
            # (MC snaps out of his temporary fantasy, Kristina wearing her dress again)"
            show sc w2krishall k35
            mc"(What on earth was that just now?? I‚Äôm starting to see things that I know I shouldn‚Äôt!)"
            k"[y_name]? Are you all right?"
            show sc w2krishall k13
            with flash
            k"You looked like you were thinking about something there for a moment?"
            mc"I uh, yeah, I‚Äôm fine. I was just thinking about what you just said before."
            mc"You mentioned something about a special treat coming my way?"
            show sc w2krishall k16
            k"Yes I did. What I meant was that the special treat could be something like good karma."
            show sc w2krishall k14
            k"You do a good deed for me, and then I guarantee that you‚Äôll get one from me in return, or maybe somebody else."
            mc"Oh‚Ä¶"
        "Don‚Äôt use it":
            show sc w2krishall k16
            k"Well what I meant was that the special treat could be something like good karma."
            show sc w2krishall k14
            k"You do a good deed for me, and then I guarantee that you‚Äôll get one from me in return, or maybe somebody else."
            mc"Oh‚Ä¶"
            # (scene continues)"
    show sc w2krishall k17
    k"Anyway, I really should get going now."
    show sc w2krishall k14
    k"I‚Äôll give you a call in a day or two so we can work out a suitable time for me to start making changes to this events room."
    k"But maybe you‚Äôll want to go over a few things with [s_name] first."
    show sc w2krishall k25
    mc"Yeah, I‚Äôm sure I‚Äôll have to."
    show sc w2krishall k19
    k"And before I go‚Ä¶"
    # (Kristina kisses the MC on the cheek)"
    play sound "sound effects/01/01/short_kiss_sound_effect.mp3"
    show sc w2krishall k28
    k"Mwah!"
    stop sound
    mc"(Oh!)"
    show sc w2krishall k16
    k"Bye [y_name]. And thanks again for thinking of me and giving me this opportunity. It‚Äôs nice knowing that I was on your mind."
    show sc w2krishall k14
    k"And thanks for also agreeing to help me out at the church again, I really appreciate it."
    mc"Uh, you‚Äôre welcome [k_name]."
    k"See you soon [y_name]. You‚Äôll be in my thoughts and prayers until I see you again."
    mc"Bye [k_name]."
    # (Behind shot of Kristina as she leaves)"
    show sc w2krishall k22
    mc"(I‚Äôll be in her thoughts? I suppose she meant it as more of a spiritual or religious thing than her actually thinking about me.)"
    mc"(And she even kissed me on the cheek! I can‚Äôt say I was expecting that, as I believed that [k_name] wasn‚Äôt the type to be affectionate with people who are not a part of her church.)"
    mc"(Perhaps I was wrong.)"
    show sc w2krishall k25
    mc"(And man she smelled good.)"
    show sc w2krishall k22
    mc"(Wait, am I even allowed to think like that about someone of the church?) "
    mc"(Hmm‚Ä¶ [s_name] isn‚Äôt back yet. I thought she would have been here by now.)"
    show sc w2krishall k27
    mc"(I guess there are a few other things I can do around the hotel until she returns‚Ä¶)"
    if v_day3_yuki_swim_call:
        # ‚ÄúAdd these lines ONLY if the player went to the mall with Yuki in the last update‚Äù"
        # (MC receives a phone call from Yuki)"
        play sound "sound effects/01/00/Cell_Phone_Ring_Sound_Effect.mp3" loop fadeout 1.0 fadein 1.0
        show sc w2krishall k33
        mc"(Oh, it‚Äôs Yuki!)"
        # [Answer it]"
        stop sound
        show sc w2krishall k29
        mc"Hello?"
        show sc w2krishall k31
        yuki"Hi [y_name], how are you?"
        mc"I‚Äôm great thanks. Yourself?"
        show sc w2krishall k32
        yuki"Yes, I‚Äôve had a great day so far."
        show sc w2krishall k29
        yuki"So I was wondering, if you‚Äôre not doing anything right now, you can come and get that scooter if you‚Äôre not busy?"
        show sc w2krishall k31
        yuki"I‚Äôm over at the family house, and I only live a few streets down from the hotel. Are you free?"
        mc"Uh, yeah, I have time. I was waiting on [s_name] to return but she‚Äôs not here yet."
        show sc w2krishall k29
        mc"I could send her a text to let her know that I‚Äôve gone to your place. I‚Äôm sure she‚Äôd be fine with it."
        show sc w2krishall k32
        yuki"Awesome! I‚Äôll message you my address when you get off this call."
        show sc w2krishall k31
        mc"Sounds good. I‚Äôll see you soon Yuki."
        yuki"Bye [y_name]."
        # (call ends)"
        show sc w2krishall k27
        mc"(That‚Äôs great news. Hopefully Yuki has enough time to show me how to ride that scooter.)"
        mc"(I‚Äôm sure [s_name] will be impressed when she sees me riding it.)"
        mc"(If only I didn‚Äôt feel so uneasy about hopping onto one of those things‚Ä¶)"
        scene black
        with dissolve
        scene black
        with Pause (2)
        jump lb_mc_visits_yuki
    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)
    jump lb_w2_k_end



label lb_mc_visits_yuki:
    # Day 4 (MOW) 19 - MC visits Yuki"
    # - this scene if you went shopping with her in v2"
    # SCENE BEGINS"
    # (the MC arrives at Yuki‚Äôs house)"
    scene sc w2yukiseaplane y01
    with dissolve
    play ambient "sound effects/02/01/small_town_sounds.mp3" loop fadeout 1.0 fadein 1.0
    mc"(This must be the place.)"
    play sound "sound effects/01/01/Door_Knock_Sound_Effect_Free.mp3"
    "(Knock, knock, knock)"
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y05
    stop sound
    # (Yuki stands out the front of her house, wearing casual, summer clothing)"
    yuki"Hey [y_name]!"
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y02
    mc"Hi Yuki. Nice place you have here."
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y07
    yuki"Yeah, my parents bought it a couple of years before I was born."
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y06
    yuki"Even though my Mom isn‚Äôt around any more..."
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y02
    yuki"I don‚Äôt think my father has any intention of leaving any time soon, which is a good thing, especially when we‚Äôre in such a great location!"
    mc"Yeah, I can see why he wouldn‚Äôt want to move."
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y03
    yuki"How was your walk down here?"
    mc"Oh, yeah, it was one of the easier walks I‚Äôve taken in recent days."
    mc"So um, about that scooter."
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y05
    yuki"Yes, the scooter. I have it in the garage for you. I just finished giving it a good polish so you should be ready to go."
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y07
    yuki"Did you have your own helmet?"
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y03
    mc"Uh, no I don‚Äôt."
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y02
    yuki"That‚Äôs no problem at all."
    yuki"You can borrow one of the spare one‚Äôs that we have. It should be a perfect fit for that big cranium of yours."
    mc"Huh?"
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y05
    yuki"I mean your skull [y_name], haha!"
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y02
    mc"Oh, right. So can I see this scooter now?"
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y03
    yuki"Sure, but, do you know how I mentioned to you the other day to keep some time free, as there was something I wanted to show you?"
    mc"Uh, vaguely. What was it?"
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y02
    yuki"I wanted to show you my seaplane. I have it down by the water if you have like half an hour free to spare?"
    mc"(Hmm‚Ä¶ I‚Äôd feel bad if I didn‚Äôt stick around, especially after Yuki has so generously offered me a scooter to use while I‚Äôm in town.)"
    mc"(However, me and [s_name] also have so much work to do at the hotel, and I want to be back there before she returns.)"
    mc"(What should I do?)"
    # [Go with her / I can‚Äôt stay]"
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y03
    menu:
        "Go with her"(wt="Best choice"):
            mc"Sure, I can spare some time."
            show sc w2yukiseaplane y05
            yuki"Awesome! Let me grab a few things and then we can walk down there together."
            show sc w2yukiseaplane y08
            if persistent.v_xray_enabled:
                show screen scr_peeping_tom("sc w2yukiseaplane y08","sc w2yukiseaplane y08x","v_pt_image_index_w2_29")
            $ yuki_points = change_stat(yuki_points,2,"Yuki")
            mc"Okay, sounds good." #+2 YUKI POINTS"
            mc"(I‚Äôm sure [s_name] won‚Äôt mind if I‚Äôm a bit late getting back. I just have to make sure Yuki shows me how to use the scooter before I leave here‚Ä¶)"
            hide screen scr_peeping_tom
            stop ambient fadeout 1.0
            # (screen goes blank)"
            # END SCENE"
            # Continues on with > Day 4 (MOW) 20 - MC spends the morning with Yuki - Seaplane lessons"
            scene black
            with dissolve
            scene black
            with Pause (2)
            jump lb_w2_yuki_seaplane
        "I can‚Äôt stay":
            show sc w2yukiseaplane y03
            mc"Oh, I‚Äôd really love to stay Yuki, but I‚Äôm kind of pressed for time today. Maybe I could take a rain check?"
            # (Yuki disappointed)"
            show sc w2yukiseaplane y04
            $ yuki_points = change_stat(yuki_points,-5,"Yuki")
            yuki"Hmm‚Ä¶ Okay, if you really need to go, then don‚Äôt let me stop you." #-5 YUKI POINTS"
            mc"(Damn‚Ä¶ I can tell she was looking forward to showing me her plane.)"
            mc"(But I can‚Äôt let the day get away from me either. Or to keep [s_name] waiting.)"
            show sc w2yukiseaplane y06
            mc"Yeah, I‚Äôm really sorry about that Yuki."
            yuki"Come with me [y_name]. I‚Äôll show you to the scooter."
            stop ambient fadeout 1.0
            # (screen goes blank)"
            scene black
            with dissolve
            scene black
            with Pause (2)
    scene sc w2yukiseaplane y25
    with dissolve
    show screen scr_rewards("sc w2yukiseaplane y25b","v_rewards_yuki_2")
    yuki"Well, there she is."
    # (A shot of the scooter)"
    hide screen scr_rewards
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y19
    yuki"Will this be suitable?"
    mc"Yeah, I‚Äôm sure this will do nicely. Again, I can‚Äôt thank you enough for this Yuki, truly."
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y24
    yuki"No problems."
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y22
    yuki"Well, if there isn‚Äôt anything else, then-"
    # (Yuki‚Äôs phone answers)"
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y26
    "(Phone rings)"
    play sound "sound effects/01/00/Cell_Phone_Ring_Sound_Effect.mp3" loop fadeout 1.0 fadein 1.0
    yuki"Oh, sorry [y_name]. I really need to answer this."
    # (Yuki answers her phone)"
    stop sound
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y27
    yuki"Hi. Yes, this is Yuki."
    # (Her face changes to one of concern)"
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y28
    yuki"Oh‚Ä¶"
    yuki"Is he okay?"
    yuki"‚Ä¶"
    yuki"I see. Okay, I‚Äôll be there as soon as I can. Thank you."
    # (Yuki‚Äôs call ends)"
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y23
    yuki"Sorry [y_name], I don‚Äôt mean to be rude, but I‚Äôm going to have to go."
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y20
    mc"Is everything okay?"
    yuki"Not exactly. That was the hospital."
    yuki"My Dad went in this morning, just as a precaution, and they‚Äôve asked me to come by."
    yuki"He decided to put me down as his next of kin after my Mom passed on you see."
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y22
    yuki"Anyway, it‚Äôs nothing major to worry about, or so they‚Äôve told me."
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y19
    yuki"It‚Äôs just some private details they need to discuss with me in person."
    mc"I see. Well don‚Äôt hang around here, go and be with your Dad."
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y18
    if persistent.v_xray_enabled:
        show screen scr_peeping_tom("sc w2yukiseaplane y18","sc w2yukiseaplane y18x","v_pt_image_index_w2_30")
    yuki"Thanks [y_name]."
    hide screen scr_peeping_tom
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y19
    yuki"Sorry to have to leave so abruptly. But we‚Äôll talk soon, okay?"
    mc"Of course."
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y22
    yuki"The keys are already in the scooter. Just pull the garage door down before you leave."
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y24
    yuki"Take care [y_name], bye!"
    # (Yuki leaves)"
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y25
    mc"(Man, I hope her Dad‚Äôs okay. I know he‚Äôs had health problems of late, but it sounded like it wasn‚Äôt overly serious.)"
    mc"(Oh shit, the scooter! I was meant to ask Yuki to show me how to ride it.)"
    mc"(How the hell am I supposed to do that, now that she‚Äôs already gone?)"
    mc"(Dammit‚Ä¶ I‚Äôm going to have to either learn how to ride it myself, or push the damn thing all the way back to the hotel.)"
    mc"(I sure as hell can‚Äôt leave it here, otherwise Yuki will wonder why I didn‚Äôt take it with me.)"
    mc"(I guess it‚Äôs not too far to push the scooter back to the hotel. Maybe I can ask [s_name] to show me how to ride it properly.)"
    mc"(But I really wanted to learn how to do that beforehand, so I could surprise her.)"
    mc"(Sigh‚Ä¶)"
    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)
    jump lb_w2_mow_mc_ashley






label lb_w2_yuki_seaplane:
    # Day 4 (MOW) 20 - MC spends the morning with Yuki - Seaplane lessons"
    # (MC walks with Yuki down to the pier)"
    scene sc w2yukiseaplane y12
    with dissolve
    play ambient "sound effects/02/01/small_town_sounds.mp3" loop fadeout 1.0 fadein 1.0
    mc"So‚Ä¶ Do you usually leave your plane down by the ocean, unattended?"
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y14
    yuki"Haha, of course not."
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y17
    show screen scr_rewards("sc w2yukiseaplane y16b","v_rewards_yuki_1")
    yuki"There‚Äôs usually someone down by the water who keeps an eye on it for me."
    hide screen scr_rewards
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y11
    yuki"And I have the key for it, so‚Ä¶"
    mc"Oh, that seems fair enough."
    # (MC and Yuki pass an Asian mother and daughter)"
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y12
    mc"This looks like a nice neighbourhood."
    # (Mother berates her teenage daughter, who exits their house and is about to leave)"
    # (The daughter is wearing very short, shorts!) "
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y29
    mot"Oh! Where are you going? You look like prostitute! Go put on pants!"
    mc"(Oh!)"
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y16
    yuki"Uh yeah, it‚Äôs a nice neighbourhood most of the time."
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y12
    mc"She sounds like a mother who is big on traditions I presume?"
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y11
    yuki"Yeah, it would seem so. I‚Äôm glad my father is a bit more relaxed with what I wear out in public nowadays."
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y12
    mc"You mean aside from the kind of bikinis that you wear?"
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y14
    yuki"Yeah, we haven‚Äôt got over that hurdle yet, but now that I‚Äôm eighteen, I hope that he will eventually understand that I can make these decisions on my own."
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y11
    mc"Good for you."
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y12
    mc"The last thing a young person wants is to have their parents still making decisions for them once they‚Äôve become an adult."
    yuki"Your Dad was like that with you too?"
    mc"Yeah, he wanted me to join the Navy, just like him. But my heart was always set on becoming a lawyer."
    mc"Even when I didn‚Äôt get the position that I wanted, he was still criticising me for supposedly making the wrong career path choice."
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y15
    yuki"That‚Äôs terrible."
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y13
    yuki"Your father should‚Äôve at least been happy that you were doing something you genuinely wanted to with your life."
    mc"I would have thought so too."
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y12
    mc"But it‚Äôs fine, I‚Äôm obviously here in Sunshine Bay for a reason."
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y11
    mc"I‚Äôm not sure what that is right now, but I‚Äôm sure it will reveal itself in time."
    # (Yuki smiles, then turns her head as she sees her plane)"
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y09
    yuki"Oh, there‚Äôs my plane."
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y30
    show screen scr_rewards("sc w2yukiseaplane y30b","v_rewards_yuki_3")
    mc"Wow‚Ä¶ She‚Äôs a beauty."
    hide screen scr_rewards
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y34
    yuki"Yeah, you should see what she‚Äôs like when she takes off!"
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y38
    yuki"Come with me, so you can see the inside of it up close‚Ä¶"
    stop ambient fadeout 1.0
    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)
    # (MC and Yuki sit inside the aircraft - Yuki sits in the main seat, the MC in the passenger‚Äôs seat)"
    play ambient "sound effects/02/01/seaplane_audio_sounds_stationary.mp3" loop fadeout 1.0 fadein 1.0
    scene sc w2yukiseaplane y40
    with dissolve
    yuki"Welcome to my cockpit [y_name]!"
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y39
    yuki"So what do you think so far?"
    mc"This is quite remarkable Yuki."
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y44
    yuki"Have you ever been in the cockpit of a plane before?"
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y39
    mc"No, I haven‚Äôt. But I‚Äôve been in the cockpit of a Navy ship."
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y40
    yuki"Oh, that must have been quite the experience!"
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y39
    mc"I guess so. I was about six or seven years old at the time so I don‚Äôt remember all that much."
    mc"I remember there being a lot more instruments and buttons compared to what you have here."
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y44
    yuki"These instruments are pretty basic compared to the bigger aircraft. Well, at least for me it is."
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y40
    yuki"So, care to go for a spin in my girl?"
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y39
    mc"What, you mean, flying? Now?"
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y44
    yuki"Yeah, why not?"
    yuki"I mean you‚Äôre already here, surely some part of you must be tempted to see what this craft can do?"
    mc"(Hmm‚Ä¶ I‚Äôd be lying if I told Yuki I wasn‚Äôt interested to find out.)"
    mc"Yeah, take her on up. I have time."
    mc"(If I return back to the hotel late, hopefully [s_name] won‚Äôt hold this experience against me.)"
    stop ambient
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y40
    play ambient "sound effects/02/01/seaplane_audio_takeoff.mp3" loop fadeout 1.0 fadein 1.0
    yuki"Okay, strap yourself in [y_name], while I get her started up."
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y45
    yuki"Okay, fuel pressure light is not lit, I‚Äôll check my flaps real quick."
    mc"Uh, okay‚Ä¶"
    # (Yuki looks out her window)"
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y40
    yuki"Looks like we are good to go."
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y44
    yuki"All right, I‚Äôll just ease things along until we really start moving‚Ä¶"
    # (Engine sound of the plane on the water starts)"
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y45
    mc"Oh man, we‚Äôre actually doing this."
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y40
    yuki"Haha, it‚Äôs great though isn‚Äôt it?"
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y42
    yuki"Here we go [y_name], any second now, and you‚Äôll be floating above the earth‚Ä¶"
    mc"(She sure seems relaxed and incredibly confident.)"
    # (Shot of the aircraft rising up off the water)"
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y46
    yuki"And we‚Äôre up in the air!"
    yuki"Let‚Äôs see how much further up I can get us, to give you an even better view of Sunshine Bay‚Ä¶"
    stop ambient fadeout 1.0
    # (screen goes blank)"
    # (scene returns with plane audio up in the air - to be added)"
    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)
    scene sc w2yukiseaplane y47
    with dissolve
    play ambient "sound effects/02/01/Seaplane_Flight_Inside.mp3" loop fadeout 1.0 fadein 1.0
    yuki"How‚Äôs the view down there [y_name]?"
    mc"It‚Äôs incredible. The town looks even more picturesque from up here."
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y55
    yuki"Yeah, it really is quite a sight to behold."
    # (show an aerial shot of Sunshine Bay from the plane)"
    mc"Wow‚Ä¶"
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y49
    yuki"It‚Äôs also perfect weather for flying. We couldn‚Äôt have asked for a better day."
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y48
    mc"Wow, we‚Äôre ascending a lot faster than I thought we would."
    yuki"Are you nervous [y_name]?"
    mc"Yeah, a little."
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y53
    yuki"So this is your first time?"
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y48
    mc"No, I've been nervous lots of times."
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y49
    yuki"Haha, no, that‚Äôs not what I meant. I mean is this your first time in a seaplane?"
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y53
    mc"Oh right, yes, yes it is."
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y48
    mc"So um, how high can one of these aircraft get up to?"
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y53
    yuki"Oh, well that depends on the make and model of each seaplane."
    yuki"This one is typically lower than a large commercial aircraft."
    yuki"For example, the Icon A5 can fly at up to around eleven thousand feet above the ground."
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y48
    yuki"But for this one that we‚Äôre currently in, they can typically cruise at about fifteen hundred feet."
    mc"Okay, so not that high then."
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y49
    yuki"You‚Äôre not afraid of heights, are you [y_name]?"
    # [No, not at all / Don‚Äôt be ridiculous]"
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y53
    menu:
        "No, not at all"(wt="Best choice"):
            show sc w2yukiseaplane y48
            mc"No, not at all. I‚Äôm cool."
            show sc w2yukiseaplane y49
            $ yuki_points = change_stat(yuki_points,2,"Yuki")
            yuki"Haha, I love your confidence." #+2 YUKI POINTS"
        "Don‚Äôt be ridiculous":
            show sc w2yukiseaplane y48
            mc"Don‚Äôt be ridiculous Yuki."
            show sc w2yukiseaplane y50
            yuki"Oh, okay."
            # (Yuki a bit taken aback by his response)"
            # (scene continues)"
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y48
    mc"But you have some parachutes packed though, right?"
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y49
    yuki"Parachutes? Nah, we don‚Äôt have any parachutes on board."
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y53
    mc"What?? How come? Didn‚Äôt you ever see Airplane!? Or La Bamba?"
    yuki"Well, I‚Äôm pretty sure you‚Äôre not a famous rock star [y_name]."
    yuki"So you should have nothing to worry about."
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y48
    mc"Are you sure you checked the wing flaps properly Yuki?"
    # (Yuki looks out the window)"
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y56
    yuki"They‚Äôre fine [y_name]."
    yuki"Actually, it looks like there‚Äôs something stuck in the propellers."
    # (screen shakes)"
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y56
    with vpunch
    mc"There is?!?"
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y49
    yuki"Haha, calm down [y_name], I‚Äôm just kidding."
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y48
    mc"I‚Äôm sorry. You‚Äôre right, I am a little nervous."
    mc"I just wish I had more control of the situation, you know?"
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y53
    yuki"Okay, well I have an idea that might help you to relax."
    mc"What do you think will help Yuki?"
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y49
    yuki"All right, well I‚Äôm going to be your instructor, and I‚Äôm gonna give you your first lesson."
    yuki"Give me your hand, and put it on my stick here."
    # (Yuki takes his hand)"
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y48
    mc"No I don‚Äôt think I should."
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y50
    yuki"You either want to learn, or you don‚Äôt."
    mc"(Ahh shit. This is so weird. What should I do?)"
    # [Kindly refuse / Give it a go]"
    menu:
        "Kindly refuse":
            show sc w2yukiseaplane y48
            mc"Actually, I‚Äôd be more comfortable if you just flew the plane Yuki."
            mc"I think I‚Äôve got myself under control now."
            show sc w2yukiseaplane y50
            yuki"Uh, okay. I was only trying to help."
            mc"I know, and I appreciate that. But maybe I shouldn‚Äôt have come up here."
            $ yuki_points = change_stat(yuki_points,-2,"Yuki")
            yuki"Yeah, maybe not." #-2 YUKI POINTS"
            mc"(What the hell is wrong with me? Why do I get like this when I‚Äôm put in this situation.)"
            show sc w2yukiseaplane y52
            yuki"I think I should probably start our descent then‚Ä¶"
            stop ambient fadeout 1.0
            # (screen goes blank)"
            # Go down to > Yuki and the MC back out the front of her house"
        "Give it a go"(wt="Best choice"):
            $ v_w2_k_yuki_plane_lessons = True
            mc"(I have to trust Yuki though, she knows what she‚Äôs doing.)"
            show sc w2yukiseaplane y48
            mc"Okay, what do I need to do?"
            show sc w2yukiseaplane y54
            yuki"Hmm... I think it will be better if we switch seats. I‚Äôll just leave this on autopilot for a few seconds."
            # (Yuki stands up)"
            show sc w2yukiseaplane y57
            if persistent.v_xray_enabled:
                show screen scr_peeping_tom("sc w2yukiseaplane y57","sc w2yukiseaplane y57x","v_pt_image_index_w2_31")
            yuki"I‚Äôm just going to swing my leg over to your side, and when I‚Äôm there, you can slide over to my seat."
            mc"(Sigh‚Ä¶) Okay."
            # (Yuki hooks her leg over to the section in front of the MC‚Äôs seat)"
            # (Yuki stands in front of where the MC is seated, bent over slightly, so her ass is presented before him)"
            yuki"Now just slide over to your seat [y_name], oh!"
            # (Yuki loses her balances and falls backwards into the MC‚Äôs lap)"
            hide screen scr_peeping_tom
            # (screen shakes)"
            show sc w2yukiseaplane y59
            with vpunch
            mc"Whoah!"
            show sc w2yukiseaplane y60
            yuki"[y_name]! I‚Äôm so sorry! Are you okay?"
            mc"Uh, yeah, I‚Äôm fine. What happened?"
            yuki"I must have lost my balance. Are you hurt?"
            # [I‚Äôm okay / I‚Äôm fine]"
            menu:
                "I‚Äôm okay":
                    show sc w2yukiseaplane y58
                    mc"I‚Äôm okay. You‚Äôre really light so I hardly felt a thing!"
                    yuki"Uh, yeah‚Ä¶"
                    show sc w2yukiseaplane y60
                    mc"(Hmm, perhaps not the best time or place to make a joke.)"
                "I‚Äôm fine"(wt="Best choice"):
                    show sc w2yukiseaplane y58
                    mc"I‚Äôm fine Yuki. It‚Äôs not everyday a girl uses me to break their fall with their ass!"
                    show sc w2yukiseaplane y61
                    $ yuki_points = change_stat(yuki_points,2,"Yuki")
                    yuki"Haha, so true [y_name]." #+2 YUKI POINTS"
                    # (scene continues)"
            # (Yuki stands back up)"
            show sc w2yukiseaplane y61
            yuki"All right, now you can try and move across to the main seat."
            # (MC slides across)"
            show sc w2yukiseaplane y62
            mc"Like this?"
            yuki"Perfect."
            show sc w2yukiseaplane y66
            yuki"Now take my hand, and put it on the control wheel here."
            # (Yuki takes the MC‚Äôs hand, placing hers over his and onto the top of the throttle lever. She leaves it on top of his and looks at the MC)"
            show sc w2yukiseaplane y67
            yuki"That‚Äôs it, get familiar with the controls, and make sure you have a decent grip on it."
            mc"(Oh boy‚Ä¶)"
            show sc w2yukiseaplane y66
            yuki"You‚Äôre going to be fine [y_name]. Can you feel the power going through it?"
            # (A shot of (Yuki‚Äôs hand on the MC‚Äôs hand)"
            mc"Yeah, I can certainly feel something there."
            # (Yuki slowly removes her hand)"
            show sc w2yukiseaplane y63
            yuki"How are you finding flying your very first plane [y_name]?"
            mc"It‚Äôs okay, but you‚Äôre helping me though."
            show sc w2yukiseaplane y65
            yuki"[y_name], I‚Äôve removed my hand from on top of yours. You‚Äôre flying the plane by yourself."
            # (MC looks down at his hand on the throttle)"
            # (screen shakes)"
            show sc w2yukiseaplane y70
            show screen scr_rewards("sc w2yukiseaplane y70b","v_rewards_yuki_4")
            mc"Oh my god! I‚Äôm flying the plane?"
            hide screen scr_rewards
            show sc w2yukiseaplane y65
            yuki"Uh-huh, and you‚Äôre doing splendidly!"
            # (a shot from outside the seaplane of the MC flying)"
            show sc w2yukiseaplane y71
            mc"This is great. I didn‚Äôt think it would be this easy. This is such a great sensation!"
            mc"I can see why you love doing this so much."
            show sc w2yukiseaplane y65
            yuki"Do you think you‚Äôd be confident enough to land it?"
            show sc w2yukiseaplane y63
            mc"Surely you can't be serious!"
            show sc w2yukiseaplane y65
            yuki"Nah, I‚Äôm just kidding [y_name]. And don't call me Shirley."
            mc"Huh?"
            yuki"Haha, it‚Äôs an old joke from that film Airplane!"
            show sc w2yukiseaplane y63
            mc"Oh‚Ä¶ I see."
            show sc w2yukiseaplane y66
            yuki"Okay, I think it‚Äôs time that we start making our descent. Maybe we should switch our seats back."
            mc"(Sigh‚Ä¶)"
            show sc w2yukiseaplane y63
            mc"Okay, if we must."
            mc"(That‚Äôs a shame. I was just starting to enjoy myself.)"
            mc"(Yuki certainly has a funny sense of humour. I like that. If only we could spend more time together.)"
            # (screen goes blank)"
            stop ambient fadeout 1.0
            scene black
            with dissolve
            scene black
            with Pause (2)
            # (scene returns with Yuki back in the main seat)"
            # (Yuki talks into her microphone)"
            play ambient "sound effects/02/01/Seaplane_Flight_Inside.mp3" loop fadeout 1.0 fadein 1.0
            show sc w2yukiseaplane y45
            yuki"Ears up, flaps down, water rudders up. Gonna take her down now [y_name]."
            show sc w2yukiseaplane y44
