    yuki"Oh, sorry [y_name]. I really need to answer this."
    mc"It‚Äôs fine, I can wait."
    stop sound
    # (Yuki answers her phone)"
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y27
    yuki"Hi. Yes, this is Yuki."
    # (Her face changes to one of concern)"
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y28
    yuki"Oh‚Ä¶"
    yuki"Is he okay?"
    yuki"‚Ä¶"
    yuki"I see. Okay, I‚Äôll be there as soon as I can. Thank you."
    # (Yuki‚Äôs call ends)"
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y23
    yuki"Sorry [y_name], I don‚Äôt mean to be rude, but I‚Äôm going to have to leave you now."
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y20
    mc"Is everything okay?"
    # (Yuki has a panicked look on her face)"
    yuki"Not exactly. That was the hospital."
    yuki"My Dad went in to see his doctor this morning, just as a precaution, and they‚Äôve asked me to come by."
    yuki"He decided to put me down as his next of kin after my Mom passed on you see."
    yuki"Anyway, it‚Äôs nothing major to worry about, or so they‚Äôve told me."
    yuki"It‚Äôs just some private details they need to discuss with me in person."
    mc"I see. Well don‚Äôt hang around here, go and be there for your Dad."
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y23
    yuki"Thanks [y_name]."
    yuki"Again, I‚Äôm so sorry to have to leave so abruptly. But we‚Äôll talk soon, okay?"
    show sc w2yukiseaplane y20
    mc"Of course."
    yuki"The keys are already in the scooter."
    yuki"Just pull the garage door down before you leave."
    yuki"Take care [y_name], bye!"
    # (Yuki leaves)"
