    mc"(Man, I hope her Dad‚Äôs okay. I know he‚Äôs had health problems of late, but it sounded like it wasn‚Äôt overly serious.)"
    mc"(Oh shit, the scooter! I was meant to ask Yuki to show me how to ride it.)"
    mc"(How the hell am I supposed to do that, now that she‚Äôs gone?)"
    mc"(Dammit‚Ä¶ I‚Äôm going to have to either learn how to ride it myself, or push the damn thing all the way back to the hotel.)"
    mc"(I sure as hell can‚Äôt leave it here, otherwise Yuki will wonder why I didn‚Äôt take it with me.)"
    mc"(I guess it‚Äôs not too far to push the scooter back to the hotel. Maybe I can ask [s_name] to show me how to ride it properly.)"
    mc"(But I really wanted to learn how to do that beforehand, so I could surprise her.)"
    mc"(Sigh‚Ä¶)"
    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)








label lb_w2_mow_mc_ashley:
    # Day 4 (MOW) 21 - MC runs into Ashley"
    # (Go right to the bottom of this scene - MC will be waiting for friend to return from the mall where she went with cousin)"
    # SCENE BEGINS"
    # (scene starts with the MC pushing the scooter alongside the beach)"
    scene sc w2ashleyjogging j01
    with dissolve
    play ambient "sound effects/01/01/Birds_in_trees_sounds_effects1.mp3" loop fadeout 1.0 fadein 1.0
    mc"(Man, it sure is hot out today.)"
    show sc w2ashleyjogging j01
    mc"(The breeze from the ocean is at least not making this completely unbearable. I‚Äôm almost there.)"
    # (MC sees someone jogging)"
    show sc w2ashleyjogging j05
    mc"(Hang on a second, isn‚Äôt that?)"
    # (MC sees Ashley jogging/power walking, in fitness gear)"
    show sc w2ashleyjogging j25
