    ash"Look, I don‚Äôt have the time to discuss this with you now, not in full detail."
    show sc w2ashleyjogging j15
    mc"So when then?"
    show sc w2ashleyjogging j16
    ash"How about sometime later this week?"
    ash"There‚Äôs a nice place in town where we can talk in private and where we can have some dinner together."
    ash"Consider it on me to make up for this abrupt ending to our talk today."
    show sc w2ashleyjogging j15
    mc"Hmm‚Ä¶ I don‚Äôt know."
    mc"I‚Äôm not sure I can get away from the hotel without lying to [s_name], or her being angry if I were to tell her the truth."
    show sc w2ashleyjogging j14
    ash"Well it‚Äôs your choice [y_name]."
