    ash"So what‚Äôs it gonna be?"
    mc"(Shit! If I‚Äôm going to help to fix things between [s_name] and her Mom, then I really need to know the answer to my question.)"
    show sc w2ashleyjogging j15
    mc"All right fine, we‚Äôll do dinner."
    show sc w2ashleyjogging j17
