    mc"(Thank god, I‚Äôm almost there.)"
    show sc w2ashleyjogging j04
    mc"(Despite not knowing how to ride this thing, at least I have a scooter now.)"
    mc"(And after seeing Ashley, she‚Äôs definitely given me a lot to think about.)"
    show sc w2ashleyjogging j02
    mc"(I definitely don‚Äôt want to keep anything from [s_name], so I‚Äôm going to tell her that I just spoke with her mother.)"
    mc"(She‚Äôs probably not going to like to hear this from me, but they need to settle their differences in order for there not be any more complications moving forward.)"
    mc"(It was so easy to be upset with Ashley for keeping me and [s_name] apart, but I can kind of understand why she did it, now that she's told me everything.)"
