    s"But you still should‚Äôve called me, as I‚Äôm sure we could‚Äôve worked something out."
    show sc w2cfrontdesk f111
    mc"I know, but she offered her scooter for me to borrow."
    show sc w2cfrontdesk f110
    mc"When you left here with [c_name], Yuki called me shortly after to see if I was free to go and pick it up."
    mc"Seeing as she doesn‚Äôt live too far from here, I thought I could go get it and have it back before you returned. It just took a little longer than I thought it would."
    mc"You don‚Äôt mind though, do you?"
    show sc w2cfrontdesk f112
