    show sc w2cfrontdesk f110
    mc"She was going for a run near the beach and just so happened to run into me. And then we got to talking."
    show sc w2cfrontdesk f111
    s"Talking about what?"
    mc"It‚Äôs a long story, but, do you remember the other day when you and your Mom had that argument after we came back from the beach?"
    s"Yeah, what about it?"
    mc"Well after you walked off, I sat down and had a long chat with her as you know. But I didn‚Äôt just ask about the hotel before and after she handed the reins over to you."
    s"What else did you talk to her about?"
