    mc"I‚Äôve wanted to ask you myself, but I know it‚Äôs not been easy for you to talk about it."
    show sc w2cfrontdesk f123
    s"Oh‚Ä¶ So, I presume you had more questions to ask my mother when you spoke to her?"
