            s"Just tell me if you do, all right?"
            mc"I will, I promise."
            mc"I want things to be good between you two, and if I can help in any way, then all the better."
            show sc w2cfrontdesk f123
            s"We‚Äôll see [y_name]."
            s"(I really want to tell him what I know, but now is definitely not the right time.)"

        "Tell her to trust you":
            # (MC grabs Friend by the side of each arm so he has her attention)"
