    nic"It‚Äôs making me really stressed out and that‚Äôs not a good thing when I have such an important case on my hands to deal with as well."
    show sc w2geonicole g16
    nic"I can‚Äôt afford to lose my focus this week."
    show sc w2geonicole g18
