    nic"Oh!"
    show sc w2geonicole g17
    geo"Ah-ha, I see."
    show sc w2geonicole g10
    nic"(Oh great! Georgina‚Äôs certainly going to use this against me later on.)"
    nic"Thank you Sir. I uh, I‚Äôm really flattered, but, I‚Äôm actually spoken for."
    "Oh, then please accept my sincerest apologies."
    "I hope you don‚Äôt mind me saying this, but I simply had to come over and meet you."
    "Anyway, after being in your presence for less than a minute, I can already tell that your guy is a very lucky man."
