    show sc w2gardening g03
    mc"I completely despise it!"
    show sc w2gardening g04
    mc"You know, when I agreed to come to Sunshine Bay to help you, this is not quite what I pictured myself doing [s_name]."
    s"I promise that you shouldn‚Äôt have to do it again [y_name], at least not for a few more weeks."
    mc"Oh man‚Ä¶"
    show sc w2gardening g03
    s"Don‚Äôt worry, once the hotel starts bringing in some business, I‚Äôll be able to hire someone part or even full-time to look after the hotel grounds and the garden beds."
    mc"I hope that‚Äôs sooner rather than later."
    # (MC‚Äôs phone goes off) Message alert sound required here"
    play sound "sound effects/01/00/Cell_phone_vibration.mp3" loop fadeout 1.0 fadein 1.0
    show sc w2gardening g07
