    mc"It‚Äôs from Victoria."
    # (MC reads it to himself)"
    vic"(Hey [y_name], how are you?)"
    vic"(I was just wondering, if you‚Äôre not doing anything tonight, did you want to hang out just like we discussed the other day?)"
    vic"(I have those tickets to that show that I mentioned, and there's also this restaurant that I‚Äôve been wanting to try out. It would be great to have a second opinion, and some company.)"
    vic"(We can also talk more about the hotel and plans for the near future over dinner.)"
    vic"(No problems if you can‚Äôt make it tonight or if this is too short of notice. Please let me know.)"
    mc"Hmm‚Ä¶"
    mc"(Damn, I forgot to tell [s_name] that I‚Äôd made plans to do something with Vicky.)"
    mc"(I just didn‚Äôt expect to hear from her so soon. I hope [s_name] doesn‚Äôt mind if I have the night off without her.)"
    show sc w2gardening g07
    s"What did she want?"
    show sc w2gardening g04
    mc"[s_name], um, I forgot to tell you this..."
    mc"But when Vicky was here the other day to check over the main kitchen, we mutually decided to do something together while I‚Äôm here in town."
    mc"And she was seeing if I was free tonight."
    show sc w2gardening g05
    s"Oh‚Ä¶ What would you two be doing together?"
    mc"She said she has tickets to some show, and there‚Äôs a restaurant that she wants me to see. It's probably so I can see first-hand what a professionally run kitchen looks like."
    mc"Vicky also said that we‚Äôd be discussing the business."
    mc"I‚Äôm sorry that I forgot to tell you about this."
    show sc w2gardening g09
    s"It‚Äôs okay. So, you definitely want to go?"
    show sc w2gardening g04
    mc"I really think I should."
    mc"And like you said, you want me to try and make friends with people while I‚Äôm here in town..."
    mc"So spending time with Vicky, someone who could be working very closely with us, seems like the ideal person for me to spend time with, don‚Äôt you think?"
    show sc w2gardening g03
