    show sc w2gardening g04
    mc"But are you going to be okay without me here tonight?"
    show sc w2gardening g08
    s"I‚Äôll be fine. I‚Äôm a big girl, and I‚Äôm sure I can keep myself occupied for a few hours while you‚Äôre out."
    s"As long she doesn‚Äôt take you to her father‚Äôs restaurant though."
    s"You might want to consider wearing a bulletproof vest under the shirt you‚Äôre going to wear for dinner [y_name]."
    show sc w2gardening g03
    mc"Oh! You don‚Äôt suppose that Vicky is going to actually take me to her father‚Äôs restaurant, do you?"
    show sc w2gardening g06
