    show sc w2gardening g03
    mc"That‚Äôs a relief."
    mc"(Could her Dad really be as terrifying as he sounds? Surely not‚Ä¶)"
    show sc w2gardening g06
    s"Anyway, you better text Vicky back and then go and take a shower [y_name]."
