    mc"(Oh shit, did I forget to call her again last night?)"
    mc"(Dammit, I better come up with a really good apology, and fast!)"
    # (Nicole‚Äôs face pops up on screen)"
    stop sound
    show sc w2gettingreadyvic v05
    mc"Hey Nicky."
    nic"Hi [y_name], is this a bad time?"
    show sc w2gettingreadyvic v06
