    show sc w2gettingreadyvic v05
    nic"Yeah um, I really needed to talk to you, it‚Äôs kind of important."
    mc"I‚Äôm so glad that you called Nicole. Even though things are going really well here, I want you to know I‚Äôve been thinking about you a lot, and-"
    # (Nicole cuts the MC off)"
    nic"I think we should see other people [y_name]‚Ä¶"
    # (screen shakes)"
    show sc w2gettingreadyvic v05
    with vpunch
    mc"What??"
    show sc w2gettingreadyvic v11
