    show sc w2gettingreadyvic v05
    mc"Wait, what are you trying to tell me Nicole? Are you‚Ä¶ Are you breaking up with me?"
    nic"No no, that‚Äôs not what I was going to say."
    nic"I realise that you‚Äôve only been away for less than a week now, but honestly [y_name], I‚Äôm not handling things as well as I thought I would."
    nic"I‚Äôve been meaning to tell you, but each time that we‚Äôve spoken like this, I‚Äôve found it difficult to bring it up in conversation."
