label lb_w2_nicole_chat_mc_1:
    nic"And you‚Äôd be letting [s_name] down if you were to do that."

label lb_w2_nicole_chat_mc_2:
    mc"What is there to solve between us Nicole?"
    show sc w2gettingreadyvic v11
    nic"Oh come on [y_name]. You know things have been far from perfect."
    show sc w2gettingreadyvic v05
    nic"The arguments, the stress, the mortgage‚Ä¶"
    nic"Then you didn‚Äôt get the job you wanted, and now I‚Äôve just been lumped with a difficult case. Plus I‚Äôm also here at home, all alone, with our shitty weather."
    nic"It‚Äôs been a hell of a lot for me to deal with in such a short space of time, and it‚Äôs finally taken its toll on me emotionally, and mentally."
    nic"But maybe this is all my fault."
    nic"Maybe I put far too much pressure on you or I was being too controlling, and if I‚Äôve done either of those things, then I‚Äôm truly sorry."
    mc"Nicky, you know how I feel about you, but whatever problems we have, I know that we can fix them together."
    nic"I‚Äôm sure we can in time [y_name]..."
    nic"However, I think that seeing as we‚Äôre going to be apart for the entire summer, maybe we should use this time to consider other alternatives, if you know what I mean?"
    mc"(Hang on, Nicole‚Äôs not suggesting what I think she is, is she?)"
    show sc w2gettingreadyvic v06
    mc"Nicky‚Ä¶. Have you been seeing someone else?"
    show sc w2gettingreadyvic v11
    nic"What? No, of course I haven‚Äôt. How could you even think that?"
    show sc w2gettingreadyvic v05
    mc"I‚Äôm sorry, I don‚Äôt know."
    mc"I‚Äôm just a little stunned. This news has come right out of the blue, and I honestly wasn‚Äôt expecting to have this conversation with you so soon after leaving home."
    nic"Again, I apologise for dumping this on you without any warning. It‚Äôs just been on my mind and I had to tell you how I really feel."
    mc"So what are you proposing that we do?"
    show sc w2gettingreadyvic v06
    mc"Are we taking a break in our relationship while I‚Äôm away for the summer? Is that it?"
    nic"Not a break as such, but I‚Äôve been contemplating the idea for us both to have an open relationship, at least until the summer is over and you return home."
    mc"An open relationship?"
    mc"You mean, you want me to start seeing other women, while you are seeing other men?"
    show sc w2gettingreadyvic v07
    nic"That‚Äôs precisely what I‚Äôm proposing."
    nic"Consider it like a three-month ‚Äúhall pass‚Äù [y_name]. However, there are some rules that I‚Äôve set for this."
    mc"Such as?"
    show sc w2gettingreadyvic v06
    nic"We both can see other people, but we need to agree to be open and honest with each other about it."
    nic"If we ask for details about who we're seeing, then we should let the other person know what they're like, and what the date was like."
    mc"Really? Are you sure about this Nicole?"
    nic"I'm positive. For this to work we need full disclosure."
    show sc w2gettingreadyvic v10
    mc"All right, what else?"
    show sc w2gettingreadyvic v06
    nic"Make it known to the person who you are interested in that you‚Äôre only looking for something casual, and nothing serious."
    mc"Okay, that‚Äôs fair enough."
    show sc w2gettingreadyvic v05
    nic"And as a recommendation, if either of us decides to, well, you know, spend the night with another person, then protection should be used."
    nic"Unless of course you definitely know for sure you‚Äôre being safe or careful without it."
    nic"But I highly suggest that you take precautions [y_name]."
    mc"Damn‚Ä¶ You really have thought all of this out, haven‚Äôt you?"
    show sc w2gettingreadyvic v06
    nic"You know me, I like to be organised."
    nic"But there‚Äôs one last thing, which is the most important rule of all."
    mc"Okay, hit me with it."
    show sc w2gettingreadyvic v05
    nic"If either of us truly believes we‚Äôve met someone that we can see ourselves being with, in a serious relationship, then we have to tell the other person."
    show sc w2gettingreadyvic v06
    mc"But if that were to happen, that would mean that you and me would be over with, wouldn‚Äôt we?"
    nic"That‚Äôs right. However, I‚Äôm willing to take my chances [y_name]."
    nic"The likeliness of finding someone in that time who could be a better fit for either of us is highly improbable."
    mc"I guess so."
    mc"(Still, I don‚Äôt know if I like this idea.) "
    show sc w2gettingreadyvic v05
    nic"Haven‚Äôt you ever wondered what life would be like [y_name] if we'd never dated, or gone to the same college, or lived together?"
    nic"Is there no part of you that is itching to find out?"
    show sc w2gettingreadyvic v06
    mc"Honestly, it‚Äôs never really crossed my mind since we‚Äôve been together Nicky. Why, have you?"
    nic"Well lately, yes I have."
    show sc w2gettingreadyvic v05
    nic"I mean, it‚Äôs not been at the forefront of my mind, but certain things that have happened since you left town that has really made me start to wonder."
    nic"I love you [y_name], I always have and I always will..."
    nic"But I think this could turn out to be a really good thing for us, and it could potentially strengthen our relationship by the time you return home."
    mc"(Sigh‚Ä¶)"
    show sc w2gettingreadyvic v06
    nic"What do you think? Is this something that you will be willing to do with me for the next few months?"
    $ v_w2_nicole_open_relationship = True
    mc"(Hmm‚Ä¶ This doesn‚Äôt seem right at all. However, what if Nicky‚Äôs right?)"
    mc"(What if having an open relationship while I‚Äôm away is the answer to all of our problems?)"
    mc"(It seems a little unorthodox, but maybe being apart from each other for a few months will be harder than I first realised.)"
    mc"(Nicole has given this plenty of thought, and maybe for good reason.)"
    mc"(If she really wants this and thinks it‚Äôs best for both of us, then maybe I should agree to this idea of hers.)"
    mc"Nicole, I agree."
    show sc w2gettingreadyvic v06
