    mc"To your terms. To all of it."
    show sc w2gettingreadyvic v05
    nic"You will?"
    show sc w2gettingreadyvic v06
    mc"Yeah. As you said, this could be a good thing for us."
    mc"And you‚Äôre right, things have been really stressful these past few months, and perhaps we‚Äôre only going to make things worse because we‚Äôre not together."
    nic"So, you‚Äôre okay with seeing other people then, just for the time while you‚Äôre away?"
    mc"(Sigh‚Ä¶)"
