    show sc w2gettingreadyvic v05
    nic"Me either. But I guess it‚Äôs not knowing what could happen is what intrigues me the most."
    mc"Yeah, I can see why you would think that."
    show sc w2gettingreadyvic v10
    nic"Babe, I‚Äôm sorry, but I gotta go. Just promise me that you‚Äôll keep in touch and let me know you‚Äôre okay."
    mc"I promise. "
    show sc w2gettingreadyvic v07
    nic"Great. I‚Äôll let you get back to what you were doing. I love you [y_name], and thank you for understanding. Enjoy yourself, I mean that."
    mc"I love you too Nicky. I‚Äôll talk to you soon."
    nic"Night [y_name]."
    # (call ends)"
