label lb_w2_mc_return_hotel:
    # Day 4 (MOW) 27 - MC returns to the hotel"
    # - Twins call MC/Friend and tell them about the fire incident while they're having breakfast"
    # - these lines if the MC DID NOT sleep with Vicky"
    # - these lines if the MC slept with Vicky"
    # SCENE BEGINS"
    # (MC arrives back inside the hotel)"
    # (MC enters the hotel TV room, sees friend sitting on a sofa reading a book)"
    scene sc w2eveninghotel h01
    with dissolve
    mc"Hey [s_name]. Great, you‚Äôre still awake!"
    show sc w2eveninghotel h02
    s"Yeah, I almost gave up on you and was going to go to bed."
    show sc w2eveninghotel h03
    s"Did you have fun with Vicky?"
    mc"Yeah, I had a great time."
    mc"The tickets she had was for a cabaret restaurant. It was a thoroughly entertaining show, and the food was very good as well."
    show sc w2eveninghotel h05
    s"Vicky knows the best places to go and all the right people in town, that‚Äôs for sure."
    show sc w2eveninghotel h02
    mc"And in even better news [s_name], Vicky has agreed to work with us in a more full-time role."
    show sc w2eveninghotel h05
    s"Oh wow! What did she say exactly?"
    show sc w2eveninghotel h03
    mc"Something along the lines of wanting to expand her options and endeavours, while also running the food truck I think."
    mc"But the most important thing is that she really wants to work with us."
    s"You see?"
    s"I told you it would be a good idea to have a night out with her."
    # (Friend‚Äôs phone rings) phone ringing audio here"
    show sc w2eveninghotel h06
    if persistent.v_xray_enabled:
        show screen scr_peeping_tom("sc w2eveninghotel h06","sc w2eveninghotel h06x","v_pt_image_index_w2_35")
    "(Phone rings)"
    play sound "sound effects/01/00/Cell_Phone_Ring_Sound_Effect.mp3" loop fadeout 1.0 fadein 1.0
    s"Oh!"
    mc"Who‚Äôs calling you this late at night?"
    # (Friend looks at her phone)"
    hide screen scr_peeping_tom
    show sc w2eveninghotel h18
    s"It‚Äôs Lily. Give me a moment [y_name]."
    stop sound
    # (Friend answers her phone) "
    show sc w2eveninghotel h15
    s"Hey Lily."
    lily"Hey [s_name], I didn‚Äôt wake you, did I?"
    s"No I was awake."
    show sc w2eveninghotel h14
    lily"Is [y_name] there with you? I have something important to discuss with you both."
    show sc w2eveninghotel h17
    s"Yeah he is. I‚Äôll put my phone on speaker."
    # (Friend sets the call to speaker)"
    show sc w2eveninghotel h07
    mc"Hi Lily."
    lily"Hey [y_name]. "
    show sc w2eveninghotel h17
    lily"Sorry to call you both so late, but Ivy and I have a huge problem on our hands."
    show sc w2eveninghotel h19
    s"Oh, what‚Äôs happened?"
    lily"Did either of you watch the local news this evening?"
    show sc w2eveninghotel h09
    s"Uh, no, no we didn‚Äôt."
    show sc w2eveninghotel h17
    lily"Okay, well you know the hotel that we invited you and [y_name] to the other night for that pre-wedding function?"
    s"Yes, of course. What about it?"
    lily"Well, it went up in flames last night!"
    show sc w2eveninghotel h21
    s"It what?? How on earth did this happen?"
    show sc w2eveninghotel h09
    lily"Do either of you remember when my sister and I spoke about finding a potential issue in the kitchen area during the party?"
    s"Uh, vaguely. How come?"
    show sc w2eveninghotel h17
    lily"Well we alerted the hotel management who said that they‚Äôd take care of some faulty wiring."
    lily"But due to some gross negligence on their part..."
    lily"Those wires were sparked by some leaking water in the kitchen, that caused the whole kitchen to be set alight..."
    lily"And that filtered through to the adjacent party venue that we were in for the pre-wedding function."
    show sc w2eveninghotel h07
    mc"Oh my god, was anybody hurt?"
    show sc w2eveninghotel h19
    lily"Thankfully no."
    lily"The fire happened in the middle of the night, and both rooms were unoccupied at the time, luckily."
    show sc w2eveninghotel h07
    mc"Was that the only reason for your call Lily?"
    lily"Not exactly [y_name]."
    show sc w2eveninghotel h17
    lily"So as you both are well aware, this wedding is a huge deal for me and Ivy, and once news gets out, there will be plenty of exposure for anyone involved with hosting the big day, as well as any of the after parties."
    lily"The wedding couple is now looking at their options, as they don‚Äôt want to cancel their big day this Saturday."
    lily"Most of their guests are already in town, and they really don‚Äôt want to have to tell them to return home."
    lily"They‚Äôre currently deciding on a new venue, and Seascape Hotel is one that‚Äôs being considered."
    show sc w2eveninghotel h09
    mc"Oh, you mean Brodie‚Äôs father‚Äôs hotel?"
    lily"Yeah, the very same. They previously weren't interested in having it there, but they are now really short on options."
    show sc w2eveninghotel h19
    s"When will they make their decision?"
    lily"Tomorrow afternoon."
    lily"However, me and Ivy want to recommend your hotel to host the wedding and the after-party."
    show sc w2eveninghotel h21
    s"Oh my god, really?"
    lily"Yeah, do you think you two can pull things together in such a short amount of time?"
    show sc w2eveninghotel h09
    s"Hmm‚Ä¶ I don‚Äôt know, can we [y_name]?"
    # [I doubt it / I believe we can]"
    menu:
        "I doubt it":
            show sc w2eveninghotel h07
            mc"I don‚Äôt know, I have my doubts. We have so much to do and not much time available to do it."
            show sc w2eveninghotel h17
            lily"Ivy and I of course will do a lot of the work, the preparation, and the wedding couple will listen to us if we make a recommendation for your hotel to play host‚Ä¶"
            lily"So that‚Äôs something to also consider."
            lily"I can‚Äôt imagine that either of you would want Brodie or his father to host such a prestigious event, would you?"
            show sc w2eveninghotel h19
            s"No, definitely not!"
            lily"This might be your only chance of snatching a hugely important event, right from under their noses."
        "I believe we can"(wt="Best choice"):
            show sc w2eveninghotel h07
            mc"If we get to work right away, I don‚Äôt see why it can‚Äôt be done."
            $ s_points = change_stat(s_points,2,s_name)
            mc"We‚Äôre going to need a lot of help though." #+2 FRIEND Points"
            show sc w2eveninghotel h17
            lily"Ivy and I, of course, will do a lot of the work, the preparation..."
            lily"And the wedding couple will listen to us if we make a recommendation for your hotel to play host."
            lily"So that‚Äôs something to also consider."
            lily"I can‚Äôt imagine that either of you would want Brodie or his father to host such a prestigious event, would you?"
            show sc w2eveninghotel h19
            s"No, definitely not!"
            lily"This might be your only chance of snatching a hugely important event, right from under their noses."
    # (scene continues)"
    show sc w2eveninghotel h09
    lily"Anyway, how about you two talk it over in the morning and either myself or Ivy will give you a call and find out if you want us to recommend your hotel to the wedding couple."
    mc"That would probably be best."
    show sc w2eveninghotel h17
    lily"Okay, again, sorry to call you both so late. I just thought I‚Äôd tell you now rather than leave it until the morning."
    show sc w2eveninghotel h16
    s"Thank you for letting us know Lily. We really appreciate it."
    lily"No problem at all. Bye guys, talk to you both tomorrow."
    s"Night Lily."
    # (call ends)"
    show sc w2eveninghotel h09
    s"Wow, hosting a celebrity wedding here at my hotel? I never ever thought it would happen."
    show sc w2eveninghotel h13
    s"Do you think we should do it [y_name], or would we be rushing things?"
    show sc w2eveninghotel h07
    mc"There are a lot of things for us to take into consideration here [s_name]."
    mc"Maybe we should discuss this over breakfast in the morning, as it‚Äôs quite late now."
    mc"But it is a huge opportunity and the kind of thing that would be a major boost for the hotel."
    show sc w2eveninghotel h09
    s"Yeah, you‚Äôre right, we should sleep on it before making a decision."
    show sc w2eveninghotel h13
    s"Speaking of which, I‚Äôm getting pretty tired, so I‚Äôm gonna go to bed."
    # (Friend kisses the MC on the cheek)"
    show sc w2eveninghotel h08
    s"You can tell me more about your ‚Äúdate‚Äù with Vicky in the morning."
    mc"It wasn‚Äôt a date."
    show sc w2eveninghotel h10
    play sound "sound effects/01/02/female_laughing_giggling.mp3" fadein 1.0
    s"Haha!"
    s"Night [y_name]."
    stop sound
    scene black
    with dissolve
    scene black
    with Pause (2)
    jump lb_w2_mc_s_sleep






